{"tid":951671,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=?? 物流公司出禁令　過年前請假當自願離職","createTime":"2018-12-22T14:01:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-23T06:14:24.000Z","uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"c93273356c80eb5a0edf98820e5e318a4fa1fa9a","tid":951671,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T14:01:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181222/photo/bkn-20181222181252675-1222_00822_001_01b.jpg?20181222200759\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181222%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181222181252675-1222_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20181222200759&h=52a3ac62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n打工仔有遇到急事及身體不適，都會向公司請假，但一間疑似是物流公司近日卻發出一張「養兵千日，用在一時」通告，要求員工由即日至農曆年30晚不要請假，否則當自動離職。通告在網上迅速流傳，有人指摘該公司無良及沒有人情味，但亦有人指由於現時正值物流旺季，認為「要求都好合理」。<br />\n<br />\n網民吳常姿於「巴打絲打 Facebook Club」專頁上載一張公司內部通告照片，通告中以「養兵千日，用在一時」為題。通告以手寫在白板上：「請各位同事不要請假，由即日開始直到年30晚(4/2/2019)。如有請假，當自動離職。」旁邊則有「永不錄用」四字，不過通告末端補充：「如真係病或者緊要事除外」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181222/bkn-20181222181252675-1222_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181222%2Fbkn-20181222181252675-1222_00822_001.html&d=Hrp0fs57trArtuevVMsA6nIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=8d34584d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181222/bkn-20181222181252675-1222_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"966687ee0afeaa72be6d1f2f110652f3a6995a01","tid":951671,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T14:01:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9b2aa50c82cd4e92d5d87243442ea0dc86b299a","tid":951671,"uid":166886,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T14:02:28.000Z","msg":"女人字<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15a3a3336c4e80a7c7d9d57b1e113643d6b049ab","tid":951671,"uid":51720,"like":0,"